cu.explanation_en: Setting the hardware log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and prevent proper hardware log output.

du.explanation_en: Setting the force 256QAM off to an out-of-range value of 2 will cause modulation configuration errors and prevent proper signal transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將強制 256QAM 關閉設定為超出範圍的值 2，會導致調製配置錯誤，並阻止正確的信號傳輸。
